Package: concise
Type: Package
Title: Minimalist data transformations supporting powerful lambda functions
Version: 0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Dominic", "Jarkey", email="dominic.jarkey@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A set of mapping and data-transformation functions leveraging a
    custom anonymous function notation that allows for direct reference to
    data variables without having to pass them explicitly.
Depends: R (>= 3.4)
